Package: magmaR
Title: Musical And General Memory Assessment
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Seb",
           family = "Silas",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sebsilas@gmail.com")
Description: magmaR helps build different types of psychological tests via the psychTestR package. There is a particular emphasis on deploying musical stimuli (e.g., musical notation, melody playback) and musical response data collection (e.g., audio and MIDI) as well as testing memory more generally. 
